{
  "id": "momentum-conservation",
  "name": "Conservation of Momentum - Elastic Collisions",
  "description": "Demonstrates the law of conservation of momentum in 1D elastic collisions. Total momentum before = Total momentum after: m₁v₁ + m₂v₂ = m₁v₁' + m₂v₂'. For elastic collisions, kinetic energy is also conserved. Experiment with different masses to see how momentum transfers!",
